column2: "What's going on...? What's wrong with this body?!"
"Why can't I sense my own power? It must be just around here..!"
"I... I am the one that stole this body 10 years ago, Dark Falz [Apprentice]!"
"You're wrong! If that were the case, then I would have given up! I would have given up a long time ago!"
"Sis, you weren't body-jacked or consumed or anything! You were abducted by the darkness!"
"That's it, remember it Yuki-nee... remember what really happened that day!"
